divs: sighting detailsi was not in chicago that day but my bf was. he was going to see his brother's graduation from the navy. he took a picture of what he thought were two brightly lit clouds on his cell phone. that is what it looked like to me too but then i looked closer. there was a darker area of the sky behind the two bright rectangle lights(not clouds). it was an invisible ufo in the shape of a rectangle\square. it took up the whole screen of his cell phone( it was his home screen photo). it looked huge and very low to the ground. i tried to get him to see what i saw but he has bad i sight. my mom took a look and could see the shadowy fig. too. i really wanted to print it but we didn't have the technoogy. it was the weirdest discovery to find the perfect shot of a rectangle ufo. i wish i could have printed it. oh well. just my luck. i'm a firm beleiver in ufos but my bf isn't. he thinks i'm crazy but i know an alien ufo when i see one. i just have this sense.
